---
title: Indian Chickpea & Veggie Filo Parcels with Lemon Yoghurt & Mixed Leaf Salad
description: Ding dong! One delivery of scrumptious Indian spiced chickpeas with roasted veggies. Careful, that filo pastry wrapping is golden crunchy and simply irresistible, it should come with a warning. As a bonus, we’re giving you a zesty lemon yoghurt to serve with the parcels. Sign on the dotted line and this delicious dish is all yours!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/indian-chickpea-veggie-parcels-e014056d.jpg
